1
00:00:19,400 --> 00:00:21,033
Why are you doing this to me?

2
00:00:21,100 --> 00:00:23,167
Is that included
in my community service?

3
00:00:23,233 --> 00:00:24,567
What do you mean?

4
00:00:24,633 --> 00:00:26,633
Why do you bring me
to those places?

5
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:28,500
You know that I have a lot
of memories there,

6
00:00:28,567 --> 00:00:29,800
memories with you.

7
00:00:29,867 --> 00:00:31,100
You want me to remember
everything.

8
00:00:31,167 --> 00:00:33,367
- Maybe...
- Don't say it.

9
00:00:33,433 --> 00:00:35,133
You know, I didn't decide
what you will do

10
00:00:35,233 --> 00:00:36,767
in your community service.

11
00:00:36,833 --> 00:00:38,933
And believe it or not,
it was already prepared

12
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:41,600
before they choose me
as your social worker.

13
00:00:41,667 --> 00:00:43,800
I'll repeat it again, Celeste,
nothing personal about it.

14
00:00:43,867 --> 00:00:45,167
With your investment,

15
00:00:45,233 --> 00:00:50,000
you're now a part of my group of
companies as a minority stake.

16
00:00:50,067 --> 00:00:51,567
Why are you doing this?

17
00:00:51,633 --> 00:00:53,100
It's about Tonito.

18
00:00:53,167 --> 00:00:54,433
What about Tonito?

19
00:00:54,500 --> 00:00:56,300
I want him back.

20
00:00:56,367 --> 00:00:58,300
You know, it's not too bad

21
00:00:58,367 --> 00:01:00,867
if you relax with your life
sometimes.

22
00:01:00,933 --> 00:01:02,733
You know, appreciate things,

23
00:01:02,800 --> 00:01:05,367
appreciate the people
who are important to you.

24
00:01:05,433 --> 00:01:06,633
Yeah, very much.

25
00:01:06,700 --> 00:01:08,800
I appreciate all the people
who are important to me,

26
00:01:08,900 --> 00:01:12,300
especially Tonito,
because he didn't leave me.

27
00:01:12,367 --> 00:01:13,733
Are you two fighting?

28
00:01:13,800 --> 00:01:14,733
- Yes.
- No.

29
00:01:14,800 --> 00:01:16,000
No, we're okay, right?

30
00:01:16,067 --> 00:01:19,033
Celeste really enjoyed her
community service today.

31
00:01:19,100 --> 00:01:20,833
Very much.

32
00:01:20,900 --> 00:01:23,033
Mikoy is very fun to be with.

33
00:01:23,100 --> 00:01:24,867
Anyway, I'll sleep very long.

34
00:01:24,933 --> 00:01:26,467
I will sleep the whole day.

35
00:01:27,633 --> 00:01:30,300
So annoying!
You know too much, Mikoy.

36
00:01:30,367 --> 00:01:32,733
You're so annoying! Oh my God,
I forgot to text...

37
00:01:32,800 --> 00:01:35,833
I forgot about Tonito.

38
00:01:40,600 --> 00:01:42,600
Oh...

39
00:01:42,700 --> 00:01:45,833
my freaking God.

40
00:01:45,900 --> 00:01:47,433
Please disregard my message.

41
00:01:47,500 --> 00:01:48,833
That's for my fiancé.

42
00:01:48,900 --> 00:01:50,967
It was a wrong send.

43
00:01:51,033 --> 00:01:52,667
Why are you grumpy?

44
00:01:52,733 --> 00:01:55,233
It was you who made a mistake
and you're angry?

45
00:01:57,600 --> 00:02:02,133
Because you are assuming, bye.
You're annoying.

46
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:06,567
Good night. Sweet dreams.

47
00:02:11,733 --> 00:02:13,067
Hello, Jamaica.

48
00:02:13,133 --> 00:02:16,300
Where is the car that you said
you rented for me?

49
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:18,300
Celeste, I tried,

50
00:02:18,367 --> 00:02:20,400
but when they found out
that it was you who requested,

51
00:02:20,467 --> 00:02:22,867
they didn't get back to me.

52
00:02:22,933 --> 00:02:26,233
I guess your accident viral
video placed you in a bad light.

53
00:02:26,300 --> 00:02:28,767
It looks like you have no other
choice, but to commute.

54
00:02:28,833 --> 00:02:29,667
No.

55
00:02:29,733 --> 00:02:31,433
Or you can go with Mikoy.

56
00:02:31,500 --> 00:02:35,300
I'd rather commute
or walk a long way,

57
00:02:35,367 --> 00:02:38,100
instead of going with Mikoy.

58
00:02:38,167 --> 00:02:40,400
Well, thank you so much,
Jamaica, for your glorious job.

59
00:02:40,467 --> 00:02:41,500
Well done.

60
00:02:43,833 --> 00:02:45,067
They're so fussy!

61
00:02:48,867 --> 00:02:50,833
I can do this.

62
00:02:50,900 --> 00:02:52,300
Happiness.

63
00:02:52,367 --> 00:02:53,467
Positive.

64
00:03:02,033 --> 00:03:04,867
You should've called her
before she left.

65
00:03:04,933 --> 00:03:08,100
I'm calling her, but I think
she didn't hear the ring.

66
00:03:08,167 --> 00:03:10,867
Let's just eat this.

67
00:03:10,933 --> 00:03:12,133
Huh?

68
00:03:12,200 --> 00:03:14,467
Is there a problem?

69
00:03:14,533 --> 00:03:18,367
I wasn't able to give this food
to Celeste.

70
00:03:18,433 --> 00:03:21,267
I'm the one who prepared this.

71
00:03:21,367 --> 00:03:23,467
You can give that to me.

72
00:03:23,533 --> 00:03:25,300
She will not eat that.

73
00:03:25,367 --> 00:03:26,767
You know her.

74
00:03:26,833 --> 00:03:29,300
This is all fruits
and vegetables.

75
00:03:29,367 --> 00:03:32,200
This is for Celeste
and not for you.

76
00:03:32,267 --> 00:03:34,533
She will eat this.

77
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:38,067
Sebastian, can you bring this
to Celeste?

78
00:03:38,133 --> 00:03:41,967
What I know is she's going
to the weaving factory.

79
00:03:43,167 --> 00:03:45,367
I'm worried if she gets hungry
later.

80
00:03:45,433 --> 00:03:49,900
I'm sure she will not eat
the food there.

81
00:03:49,967 --> 00:03:51,067
Are you sure, Father?

82
00:03:51,133 --> 00:03:54,133
She might just throw it away.

83
00:03:54,233 --> 00:03:55,833
There you go again.

84
00:03:55,900 --> 00:03:59,433
Who knows, come on.

85
00:03:59,500 --> 00:04:00,467
Okay.

86
00:04:15,567 --> 00:04:18,867
That's okay. See you again soon.

87
00:04:18,933 --> 00:04:22,267
Sebastian, you should go.

88
00:04:22,333 --> 00:04:24,433
Oh my...

89
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:28,067
Okay.

90
00:04:28,167 --> 00:04:30,533
- You better go.
- Your son has a side trip.

91
00:04:30,867 --> 00:04:31,867
He's blushing.

92
00:04:31,933 --> 00:04:34,333
Who is he texting?

93
00:04:39,333 --> 00:04:42,667
We need to be fast,
so we can send the editor the...

94
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:49,900
Miss Celeste, good thing
you're here.

95
00:04:49,967 --> 00:04:51,233
Mikoy is looking for me?

96
00:04:51,300 --> 00:04:52,433
He's excited?

97
00:04:58,100 --> 00:04:59,867
I'm the one looking for you.

98
00:05:01,167 --> 00:05:03,067
Mikoy can't come.

99
00:05:03,133 --> 00:05:05,033
And he sent me as a replacement.

100
00:05:34,533 --> 00:05:36,700
Good morning.

101
00:05:36,767 --> 00:05:40,933
My name is Evangeline Macapugay.

102
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:44,133
Ms. Vangie for short.

103
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:48,500
I'm your temporary probationary
officer, Celeste.

104
00:05:50,867 --> 00:05:54,333
It's Celeste, silent E.

105
00:05:54,400 --> 00:05:55,700
Right.

106
00:05:57,900 --> 00:06:01,167
Didn't they send you
a dress code here?

107
00:06:01,233 --> 00:06:03,967
It seems Mikoy is very kind
to you.

108
00:06:05,133 --> 00:06:07,367
It's presentable.

109
00:06:07,467 --> 00:06:09,300
You should remove your chains.

110
00:06:10,467 --> 00:06:11,633
What?

111
00:06:11,700 --> 00:06:14,133
- That.
- It's a watch.

112
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:16,533
Even your leash.

113
00:06:18,267 --> 00:06:20,133
Come again?

114
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:21,800
I'm not a dog.

115
00:06:21,867 --> 00:06:23,600
Whatever that is on your neck.

116
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:26,700
What's wrong?

117
00:06:26,767 --> 00:06:31,067
You are doing community service,
not a fashion show.

118
00:06:33,967 --> 00:06:37,700
We'll start at 9 am sharp
and finish at 5 pm, sharp.

119
00:06:37,767 --> 00:06:40,733
You have an hour lunchtime
at 12 noon, sharp.

120
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:43,467
And a fifteen-minute break
at 3 pm sharp.

121
00:06:43,567 --> 00:06:46,167
And thirty-second water breaks
every hour.

122
00:06:46,233 --> 00:06:47,967
Phone is not allowed at work.

123
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,967
It's already 9 am.

124
00:06:53,033 --> 00:06:55,300
You can start.

125
00:06:55,367 --> 00:06:56,667
Any questions?

126
00:06:58,800 --> 00:06:59,800
Nothing.

127
00:07:01,067 --> 00:07:05,200
Ms. Vangie, when will Mikoy
come back?

128
00:07:05,267 --> 00:07:08,833
Will you be my probation
officer forever?

129
00:07:08,900 --> 00:07:10,933
Mikoy is on leave,

130
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:16,433
and while he's on leave,
I will be with you.

131
00:07:16,533 --> 00:07:19,433
I'm totally different
from Mikoy, Celeste.

132
00:07:19,500 --> 00:07:21,700
So you should be good.

133
00:07:21,767 --> 00:07:23,067
Now, move.

134
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:28,733
You should remove
your pearl earrings.

135
00:07:46,400 --> 00:07:47,467
He's not here.

136
00:07:48,533 --> 00:07:50,433
Mikoy!

137
00:07:50,500 --> 00:07:52,500
Mikoy.

138
00:07:52,567 --> 00:07:54,500
Mikoy?

139
00:07:54,567 --> 00:07:55,567
He is ignoring me.

140
00:07:55,633 --> 00:07:57,433
Handsome...

141
00:07:57,500 --> 00:07:59,433
There you go.

142
00:07:59,500 --> 00:08:02,700
You're really something, Mikoy.

143
00:08:02,767 --> 00:08:04,033
You need something, right?

144
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,600
This is my route today.

145
00:08:07,667 --> 00:08:08,833
Okay.

146
00:08:08,900 --> 00:08:12,300
By the way, why are you not
in cuz' community service?

147
00:08:12,367 --> 00:08:14,767
I'm on leave today.
Someone else is assigned to her.

148
00:08:14,833 --> 00:08:16,800
So, how are you?

149
00:08:18,367 --> 00:08:22,933
Well with God's mercy,
we're okay.

150
00:08:23,033 --> 00:08:25,667
We fought last night.

151
00:08:25,733 --> 00:08:26,733
What?

152
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:28,000
Why?

153
00:08:28,067 --> 00:08:29,967
She changed a lot.

154
00:08:30,033 --> 00:08:32,400
We argued last night.

155
00:08:32,467 --> 00:08:33,633
She really changed a lot.

156
00:08:33,700 --> 00:08:36,200
She just wore heels and
she thinks highly of herself.

157
00:08:36,267 --> 00:08:37,667
Not really.

158
00:08:37,733 --> 00:08:40,100
Well, she wears fashionable
clothes

159
00:08:40,167 --> 00:08:42,200
and she's very good
at speaking English.

160
00:08:42,267 --> 00:08:45,167
But she's still the same.
She's still an Uragon .

161
00:08:45,233 --> 00:08:48,300
I even made her eat
chili ice cream.

162
00:08:48,367 --> 00:08:50,167
What's with you?

163
00:08:50,233 --> 00:08:52,900
She was just forced.

164
00:08:52,967 --> 00:08:54,800
She's totally different.

165
00:08:56,367 --> 00:08:58,867
But maybe it was also my fault.

166
00:08:58,933 --> 00:09:01,500
Maybe if I didn't leave her
in Manila,

167
00:09:01,567 --> 00:09:04,167
I could've guided her properly.

168
00:09:04,233 --> 00:09:06,133
You're too hard on yourself.

169
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:07,233
You're too much.

170
00:09:07,300 --> 00:09:09,667
No, I'm serious.

171
00:09:09,733 --> 00:09:11,567
But I won't give up on her.

172
00:09:11,633 --> 00:09:14,633
I will introduce her
to the old Celeste.

173
00:09:45,800 --> 00:09:48,933
Do you know Ms. Vangie?

174
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:51,433
Not personally,
but she is known here.

175
00:09:51,500 --> 00:09:53,833
She's strict.

176
00:09:53,900 --> 00:09:55,833
She's a spinster.

177
00:09:57,500 --> 00:10:02,033
That's how it is,
if you are a spinster.

178
00:10:02,133 --> 00:10:06,500
Yes, it's sad when there's
no one to hug you at night.

179
00:10:06,567 --> 00:10:07,967
How can she have a boyfriend?

180
00:10:08,033 --> 00:10:09,700
She's very toxic.

181
00:10:09,767 --> 00:10:12,033
She's negative.

182
00:10:12,100 --> 00:10:14,967
You should find her a guy from
Manila that she can date with.

183
00:10:15,033 --> 00:10:19,000
Hey, before her you should
prioritize us, single mothers.

184
00:10:19,067 --> 00:10:20,400
Oh my...

185
00:10:20,467 --> 00:10:22,933
Maybe you can do that Celeste.

186
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:25,800
I know a lot of models there.

187
00:10:25,867 --> 00:10:28,400
What is your type?

188
00:10:28,467 --> 00:10:32,167
I'll teach you to install
a dating app.

189
00:10:32,233 --> 00:10:33,800
All you do is just match.

190
00:10:33,867 --> 00:10:35,267
I told you.

191
00:10:38,033 --> 00:10:40,333
Be quiet!

192
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:44,067
This is a workplace,
not a coffee shop.

193
00:11:03,567 --> 00:11:07,100
I hate to burst your bubble,
Vivian.

194
00:11:07,167 --> 00:11:09,267
But have you seen this post

195
00:11:09,367 --> 00:11:12,567
about Celeste's
community service?

196
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:20,367
Unbelievable.

197
00:11:20,433 --> 00:11:24,733
God, I'm mistaking pleasure
in her misfortunes already.

198
00:11:24,800 --> 00:11:26,833
Let her enjoy it.

199
00:11:26,900 --> 00:11:28,267
That's her last.

200
00:11:28,333 --> 00:11:31,433
Now that I'm back in your
company as a stakeholder,

201
00:11:31,500 --> 00:11:35,200
Tonito and I will have
a smaller world.

202
00:11:36,433 --> 00:11:38,700
Well, it would be a lot easier

203
00:11:38,767 --> 00:11:41,567
if your family
will be complete again.

204
00:11:41,667 --> 00:11:44,133
You deserve my brother's love,
Aurelia,

205
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:46,100
but you should act right away.

206
00:11:46,167 --> 00:11:50,367
I miss the good old times
between me and Tonito, Vivian.

207
00:11:50,433 --> 00:11:53,767
Every time I see him
and Celeste together,

208
00:11:53,833 --> 00:11:55,833
I remember the two of us
back then.

209
00:11:55,900 --> 00:11:58,433
I miss the way he looks at me.

210
00:11:58,500 --> 00:12:02,167
I miss the way he would
tuck my hair behind my ear,

211
00:12:02,233 --> 00:12:04,633
every time the wind blew on me.

212
00:12:04,700 --> 00:12:08,700
I miss the way he would hold
my hands to warm them,

213
00:12:08,767 --> 00:12:11,233
whenever I'm nervous.

214
00:12:12,667 --> 00:12:15,300
I want to experience them
all again.

215
00:12:17,267 --> 00:12:22,000
If I were to set myself up
for another rejection,

216
00:12:22,067 --> 00:12:25,400
it must be for something worth
fighting for.

217
00:12:25,467 --> 00:12:27,300
I still love Tonito...

218
00:12:28,500 --> 00:12:30,433
more than I would ever admit.

219
00:12:32,567 --> 00:12:36,733
That's why I don't mind getting
rejected over and over again

220
00:12:36,800 --> 00:12:38,367
as long as it's for him.

221
00:13:04,933 --> 00:13:06,767
Hello, Love?

222
00:13:06,833 --> 00:13:07,900
How are you?

223
00:13:09,800 --> 00:13:12,300
Oh my God,
my life is super surreal.

224
00:13:12,367 --> 00:13:17,600
Imagine, the city hall replaced
the officer assigned to me.

225
00:13:17,667 --> 00:13:18,967
They gave me a dictator.

226
00:13:19,033 --> 00:13:23,000
And not just that, she asked me
to remove my accessories.

227
00:13:23,100 --> 00:13:25,933
I feel so naked.

228
00:13:27,367 --> 00:13:28,433
Don't worry.

229
00:13:28,500 --> 00:13:30,667
You're still beautiful
whatever you do.

230
00:13:30,733 --> 00:13:31,367
Thanks, Love.

231
00:13:31,433 --> 00:13:34,067
I wish you were here.

232
00:13:34,133 --> 00:13:35,467
I miss you.

233
00:13:35,533 --> 00:13:37,267
I miss you too.

234
00:13:37,333 --> 00:13:38,633
When you come back to Manila,

235
00:13:38,700 --> 00:13:42,533
we will push through our world
tour with your staff.

236
00:13:42,600 --> 00:13:44,933
Thank you. I just so...

237
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:47,067
I feel so violated. And then...

238
00:13:47,133 --> 00:13:49,100
they asked me to do
a lot of things.

239
00:13:49,167 --> 00:13:51,367
And I have a lot
of water break...

240
00:13:51,433 --> 00:13:54,767
Didn't I tell you it's not
allowed to accept calls

241
00:13:54,867 --> 00:13:56,367
while on duty?

242
00:13:56,433 --> 00:13:59,500
What do you not understand?

243
00:14:04,767 --> 00:14:06,167
I'll call you back.

244
00:14:06,233 --> 00:14:07,267
Okay.

245
00:14:11,533 --> 00:14:12,667
I'm sorry, Ms. Vangie.

246
00:14:12,733 --> 00:14:15,667
It was an emergency.

247
00:14:15,733 --> 00:14:19,700
So flirting with a boyfriend
is now an emergency.

248
00:14:19,767 --> 00:14:22,367
Ms. Vangie, I'm sorry.
But I'm not flirting.

249
00:14:22,433 --> 00:14:24,200
I was just reporting for duty,

250
00:14:24,267 --> 00:14:27,767
and plus, he's not my boyfriend.
He's my fiancé.

251
00:14:27,833 --> 00:14:29,567
As if she knows the difference.

252
00:14:29,667 --> 00:14:30,967
I heard that.

253
00:14:33,100 --> 00:14:34,733
Okay, Ms. Vangie.

254
00:14:34,800 --> 00:14:36,700
I'm really, really sorry.

255
00:14:36,767 --> 00:14:39,967
I'll add one hundred hours
to your community service.

256
00:14:40,033 --> 00:14:41,067
What?

257
00:14:42,167 --> 00:14:43,500
Ms. Vangie...

258
00:14:43,567 --> 00:14:45,567
okay, let's start again.

259
00:14:45,633 --> 00:14:46,333
I'm...

260
00:14:46,400 --> 00:14:50,000
I'm really, sincerely sorry.

261
00:14:50,067 --> 00:14:51,467
I just have so much...

262
00:14:51,533 --> 00:14:53,733
you know, I have a career
in Manila.

263
00:14:53,800 --> 00:14:56,167
I have a fiancé waiting for me.
I'm supposed to travel.

264
00:14:56,233 --> 00:14:57,933
I'm getting married.

265
00:14:58,000 --> 00:14:58,733
You can't...

266
00:14:58,800 --> 00:15:00,367
I...

267
00:15:00,433 --> 00:15:02,133
here you can have my phone.

268
00:15:02,233 --> 00:15:03,267
It's so nice.

269
00:15:03,333 --> 00:15:04,733
You can have it.

270
00:15:04,800 --> 00:15:06,367
It's new.

271
00:15:06,433 --> 00:15:08,400
Just take back my punishment,
please.

272
00:15:08,467 --> 00:15:09,967
I'm so, so sorry.

273
00:15:10,033 --> 00:15:12,167
- I really do apologize.
- No.

274
00:15:12,233 --> 00:15:14,033
My decision is final.

275
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:18,500
Wait, Miss Vangie.

276
00:15:18,567 --> 00:15:22,000
Ms. Vangie, you can't do this
to me.

277
00:15:22,067 --> 00:15:23,600
I will appeal in the city hall.

278
00:15:23,667 --> 00:15:27,967
I mean I feel harassed,
bullied, violated.

279
00:15:28,033 --> 00:15:31,100
What you did is a clear
rule violation.

280
00:15:31,167 --> 00:15:34,833
Maybe you have forgotten
that you have a case.

281
00:15:34,900 --> 00:15:37,433
Even if we go
to the Supreme Court,

282
00:15:37,533 --> 00:15:40,400
between the two of us,
they will side with me.

283
00:15:40,467 --> 00:15:41,533
You know...

284
00:15:41,600 --> 00:15:43,167
You know what?

285
00:15:43,233 --> 00:15:45,433
You...

286
00:15:45,500 --> 00:15:46,433
You...

287
00:15:48,967 --> 00:15:50,000
You're right.

288
00:15:55,700 --> 00:15:56,767
Get back to work.

289
00:16:10,400 --> 00:16:12,233
That Vangie is too much.

290
00:16:12,300 --> 00:16:14,333
She is very strict.

291
00:16:14,400 --> 00:16:16,133
Are you okay, Celeste?

292
00:16:26,433 --> 00:16:27,667
You know, Mikoy,

293
00:16:27,733 --> 00:16:32,500
you can't blame Celeste
for why she became like that.

294
00:16:32,567 --> 00:16:34,167
With all the things
she had gone through before,

295
00:16:34,233 --> 00:16:37,600
she reached whatever
she has right now.

296
00:16:37,667 --> 00:16:39,700
You witnessed all that, right?

297
00:16:39,767 --> 00:16:40,900
That's the thing.

298
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:43,700
Manila became bad for her.

299
00:16:43,767 --> 00:16:47,833
But she acts now as if she's
a legitimate native of Manila.

300
00:16:47,900 --> 00:16:50,433
She seemed ashamed
of where she came from.

301
00:16:50,500 --> 00:16:52,200
She no longer speaks Bicolano.

302
00:17:00,600 --> 00:17:01,967
Hello, Ms. Vangie?

303
00:17:03,467 --> 00:17:05,533
How can you handle Celeste?

304
00:17:07,200 --> 00:17:09,267
Why? What happened?

305
00:17:09,333 --> 00:17:11,733
She doesn't know
how to follow the rules.

306
00:17:11,800 --> 00:17:13,600
She complains a lot.

307
00:17:13,667 --> 00:17:19,367
She's the most troublemaker of
all cases that I have handled.

308
00:17:19,467 --> 00:17:22,367
Take it easy with Celeste.

309
00:17:22,433 --> 00:17:24,600
I want to be lenient with her,

310
00:17:24,667 --> 00:17:27,233
if she only committed
a minor offense.

311
00:17:27,300 --> 00:17:30,700
The thing is, she damaged
the galleon replica

312
00:17:30,767 --> 00:17:32,233
and her attitude is like that.

313
00:17:34,033 --> 00:17:36,700
I'm planning to make
a recommendation to Mayor.

314
00:17:36,767 --> 00:17:38,967
That is to push through
with the case against her.

315
00:17:39,033 --> 00:17:42,333
No, Celeste is still an Uragon .

316
00:17:42,400 --> 00:17:44,433
She is just a little
troublemaker.

317
00:17:44,500 --> 00:17:46,800
Have patience with her, please.

318
00:17:46,867 --> 00:17:48,500
Okay, Mikoy.

319
00:17:48,600 --> 00:17:50,200
I'll think about it first.

320
00:17:53,167 --> 00:17:55,033
What did cuz do this time?

321
00:17:56,433 --> 00:17:57,433
Huge.

322
00:17:59,000 --> 00:17:59,933
Huh?

323
00:18:03,800 --> 00:18:06,167
It's so annoying!

324
00:18:06,233 --> 00:18:08,200
Just because she can do that
to me.

325
00:18:09,467 --> 00:18:10,633
What?

326
00:18:10,700 --> 00:18:12,333
She can do that to me easily?

327
00:18:12,400 --> 00:18:14,833
I've been through many fights
in my life before.

328
00:18:14,900 --> 00:18:16,700
I'm not scared of her.

329
00:18:16,767 --> 00:18:19,067
If she's outside,
she better be ready for me.

330
00:18:19,133 --> 00:18:21,000
She better be ready for me.

331
00:18:23,067 --> 00:18:24,200
A hundred hours...

332
00:18:24,267 --> 00:18:26,333
One hundred hours.

333
00:18:26,400 --> 00:18:29,733
What will I do here
for one hundred hours?

334
00:18:29,800 --> 00:18:31,367
What if I beg her?

335
00:18:31,433 --> 00:18:33,000
I'll tell her I'm so sorry.

336
00:18:33,067 --> 00:18:34,300
I'm sure,

337
00:18:34,367 --> 00:18:39,833
underneath that tough exterior,
there's really a gentle heart.

338
00:18:39,900 --> 00:18:42,367
No, why would I do that?

339
00:18:42,433 --> 00:18:44,800
She's overreacting.
She has the nerve.

340
00:18:44,867 --> 00:18:46,333
Why would I beg her?

341
00:18:46,400 --> 00:18:48,467
Don't she dare get near me?

342
00:18:48,533 --> 00:18:49,533
Don't she dare?

343
00:18:49,600 --> 00:18:54,233
- If she gets near me, I'll...
- Celeste?

344
00:18:54,300 --> 00:18:56,300
Don't talk to me, not now.

345
00:18:56,400 --> 00:18:58,867
I'm upset. Don't come near me.

346
00:18:58,933 --> 00:19:00,867
Don't ever come near me.

347
00:19:04,300 --> 00:19:05,400
Sebastian?

348
00:19:07,000 --> 00:19:09,533
Sorry, sorry.

349
00:19:10,700 --> 00:19:12,067
What are you doing here?

350
00:19:13,400 --> 00:19:14,900
Father asked me
to bring that to you.

351
00:19:14,967 --> 00:19:16,600
You forgot it.

352
00:19:16,667 --> 00:19:18,733
Don't get mad at me, please.

353
00:19:18,800 --> 00:19:19,633
I'm not mad at you.

354
00:19:19,700 --> 00:19:20,800
I'm pissed off with someone.

355
00:19:20,867 --> 00:19:21,800
Anyway...

356
00:19:23,267 --> 00:19:24,167
what is that?

357
00:19:25,367 --> 00:19:26,467
It's your food.

358
00:19:26,533 --> 00:19:27,767
Father cooked that.

359
00:19:27,833 --> 00:19:31,433
Can you please remind them
that I don't eat this?

360
00:19:31,533 --> 00:19:33,400
And besides, I'm not a child.

361
00:19:33,467 --> 00:19:35,333
I don't need him
to do this for me.

362
00:19:36,800 --> 00:19:39,067
Okay, so I'll just take it home.

363
00:19:39,133 --> 00:19:40,600
Oh, it's...

364
00:19:40,667 --> 00:19:42,800
It's fine. Just leave it there.

365
00:19:42,867 --> 00:19:45,133
I'll just give
that to my co-workers.

366
00:19:45,200 --> 00:19:46,167
Bye, Celeste.

367
00:20:28,133 --> 00:20:29,733
Hello!

368
00:20:29,800 --> 00:20:30,800
Hi!

369
00:20:30,867 --> 00:20:31,967
Hi.

370
00:20:33,500 --> 00:20:35,533
Can I take a selfie?

371
00:20:35,633 --> 00:20:36,933
Yes, of course.

372
00:20:48,033 --> 00:20:50,833
There, thank you.

373
00:20:50,900 --> 00:20:56,067
I wanted to approach you,
but I'm shy.

374
00:20:57,300 --> 00:21:00,567
I always copy your OOTD
(Outfit of the Day)

375
00:21:00,633 --> 00:21:03,067
because you are my idol.

376
00:21:04,900 --> 00:21:09,533
I always copy that,
but it doesn't suit me.

377
00:21:09,633 --> 00:21:12,100
What's with you?
You're beautiful.

378
00:21:12,167 --> 00:21:13,967
You know you can be a model.

379
00:21:14,033 --> 00:21:16,133
Your lips are very beautiful.

380
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:19,200
You can be a beauty queen
if you want to.

381
00:21:20,467 --> 00:21:23,333
My father stopped me

382
00:21:23,400 --> 00:21:26,033
from joining the local beauty
pageants.

383
00:21:26,100 --> 00:21:28,533
He said we will only
spend money.

384
00:21:28,600 --> 00:21:32,100
He said I will not win
because I'm dark-skinned.

385
00:21:33,200 --> 00:21:35,600
That's too much.

386
00:21:35,667 --> 00:21:37,733
Don't believe that.

387
00:21:37,800 --> 00:21:43,000
You know, your uniqueness will
make you stand out in the crowd.

388
00:21:43,100 --> 00:21:44,100
Really?

389
00:21:44,167 --> 00:21:45,233
Yes, of course.

390
00:21:46,433 --> 00:21:50,700
But that is my dream
and my mother's.

391
00:21:53,767 --> 00:21:57,400
A dream can be possible.
Just keep trying.

392
00:21:57,467 --> 00:21:59,667
Don't believe what others
are saying.

393
00:21:59,733 --> 00:22:02,767
Don't let anyone rain
on your parade, okay?

394
00:22:03,900 --> 00:22:05,967
Okay, thank you.

395
00:22:06,033 --> 00:22:07,233
You should go back there.

396
00:22:07,300 --> 00:22:08,600
- Okay.
- Wait.

397
00:22:12,800 --> 00:22:14,300
You know this is my favorite.

398
00:22:15,367 --> 00:22:16,900
You can have this.

399
00:22:18,433 --> 00:22:19,800
This is mine?

400
00:22:19,867 --> 00:22:21,233
Yes.

401
00:22:22,067 --> 00:22:23,167
You should wear this.

402
00:22:23,233 --> 00:22:26,300
Wait, Ms. Vangie might see this.

403
00:22:26,367 --> 00:22:29,000
Here. Someday when you walk
the ramp,

404
00:22:29,067 --> 00:22:30,800
I want to see you wearing that.

405
00:22:30,867 --> 00:22:32,733
Thank you so much.

406
00:23:08,000 --> 00:23:11,367
I hope this is the last time
that I will confiscate that.

407
00:23:12,333 --> 00:23:13,667
Thank you, Madam.

408
00:23:14,533 --> 00:23:16,067
And my punishment?

409
00:23:17,133 --> 00:23:18,400
It will still push through.

410
00:23:19,533 --> 00:23:24,700
Okay. Well, thank you so much,
Madam, for returning my phone.

411
00:23:24,800 --> 00:23:27,867
You're such an angel.

412
00:23:28,900 --> 00:23:32,433
We're done for the day.
Don't be late tomorrow.

413
00:23:32,500 --> 00:23:35,767
Do we understand each other?

414
00:23:37,300 --> 00:23:40,300
Don't worry, I'll be here
on the dot, Madam.

415
00:23:42,367 --> 00:23:43,600
Is Mikoy still on leave?

416
00:23:43,667 --> 00:23:46,067
Unfortunately, yes.

417
00:23:46,133 --> 00:23:47,967
That's why, I'm still
your guardian.

418
00:23:49,167 --> 00:23:50,533
Such a delight.

419
00:23:50,600 --> 00:23:51,600
See you tomorrow.

420
00:23:53,667 --> 00:23:54,633
See you.

421
00:24:02,633 --> 00:24:04,267
The placement is ugly.

422
00:24:23,633 --> 00:24:27,800
I'm glad you're not discouraged
to get close to your daughter.

423
00:24:27,867 --> 00:24:31,067
I just hope that she
will soften slowly.

424
00:24:31,167 --> 00:24:33,467
I thought after a long time,

425
00:24:33,533 --> 00:24:35,700
my longing for you will subside,
Mother.

426
00:24:35,767 --> 00:24:37,733
This place is so different
without you.

427
00:24:37,800 --> 00:24:40,233
I can never call this place
home again.

428
00:24:40,300 --> 00:24:42,100
I'm not allowed to use a phone,
not allowed to talk to someone.

429
00:24:42,167 --> 00:24:44,233
It's also not allowed
for someone to visit me?

430
00:24:44,300 --> 00:24:45,300
Am I in a labor camp?

431
00:24:45,367 --> 00:24:48,333
You know honestly,
this is not fair.

432
00:24:48,400 --> 00:24:51,833
Oh my, is what I'm seeing real
or am I just dreaming?

433
00:24:51,900 --> 00:24:52,967
It's so cool.

434
00:24:53,033 --> 00:24:55,033
Oh my God. The screen though.

435
00:24:55,100 --> 00:24:57,267
You should do your work
properly, Celeste.

436
00:24:57,333 --> 00:24:58,933
That is not what Sorsorguenos
(People from Sorsogon) do.

437
00:24:59,000 --> 00:25:00,100
Yes, Sir.

438
00:25:00,167 --> 00:25:01,367
You've been here for a long time

439
00:25:01,433 --> 00:25:02,567
and this is all
you accomplished?

440
00:25:02,667 --> 00:25:04,733
You are full of drama.

441
00:25:04,800 --> 00:25:06,267
The signs are clear.

442
00:25:06,333 --> 00:25:07,300
Aurelia wants you back.

443
00:25:07,367 --> 00:25:09,033
No woman will make an effort
like that,

444
00:25:09,100 --> 00:25:10,400
if she doesn't like you.

445
00:25:10,467 --> 00:25:13,500
She invested in your business
and she treated you for lunch.

446
00:25:13,567 --> 00:25:15,767
Are you and Celeste
really getting married?

447
00:25:15,833 --> 00:25:16,967
Where is this coming from?

448
00:25:17,033 --> 00:25:19,100
Are you sure about her?

449
00:25:19,167 --> 00:25:20,667
You can have this.

450
00:25:20,733 --> 00:25:21,900
Thank you.

451
00:25:21,967 --> 00:25:23,900
Wait, I like that.

452
00:25:23,967 --> 00:25:27,367
So you'll accept my gift,
but not me?

453
00:25:28,633 --> 00:25:30,733
Celeste is family also now.

454
00:25:30,800 --> 00:25:33,400
Not unless I accept her
as your wife...

455
00:25:34,433 --> 00:25:35,800
which will never happen.

456
00:25:35,900 --> 00:25:37,467
Why are you doing this?

457
00:25:37,533 --> 00:25:39,400
I know that you said
it's just work.

458
00:25:39,467 --> 00:25:42,600
And I get that,
but do you still love me?

459
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:46,233
Yes or no?

460
00:25:46,300 --> 00:25:47,967
Do you still love, Mikoy?
